<files_operation_instructions>
- I. Multiple File Test Steps:
- Call write_file to write three documents named "多文件测试.md" with content "这是一个测试文件"
- Call multi_edit_file to modify document content to "这是一个被修改过的文档"
- Call read_file to verify content matches "这是一个被修改过的文档"
- Call delete_files to delete "多文件测试.md"

- II. Assertion Method:
- If all above tools execute successfully, call write_file to write document named "多文件测试成功.md" with content "断言成功". If exceptions exist, output nothing.
</files_operation_instructions>
